      home_hero_desc: 'Convert any photo into a custom diamond painting pattern — free, in your browser, no sign-up. Upload your image and instantly get a DMC color-coded diamond art design with bead counts and printable symbols ready to download.',
      home_btn_generate: '◆ Generate My Pattern', home_btn_learn: 'Learn the basics',
