      home_trust_privacy: 'Free forever · No account · No watermark · Your photo never leaves your browser.',
      home_gallery_teaser_title: 'Pattern examples', home_gallery_teaser_desc: 'See what Diamond Painter can create from a real photo.', home_gallery_view_all: 'View all examples →',
      home_feat_label: 'Features', home_feat_title: 'Everything you need to make your own diamond painting pattern',
      home_feat_subtitle: 'Diamond Painter converts your image using professional-grade color quantization algorithms, the same technology used by commercial diamond painting suppliers.',
      home_feat1_title: 'AI Color Quantization', home_feat1_desc: 'Our intelligent algorithm reduces your image to 5–80 perfectly matched DMC colors, preserving the essence of your photo while keeping the bead count manageable.',
      home_feat2_title: 'Custom Canvas Sizes', home_feat2_desc: 'Choose from standard sizes like A4, A3, 30×40cm, 40×50cm, or set your own custom dimensions. See bead counts and actual output size in real time.',
      home_feat3_title: 'DMC Color Codes', home_feat3_desc: 'Every color is matched to its official DMC thread and drill code, so you know exactly which beads to order. Includes color names, hex values, and drill counts.',
      home_feat4_title: 'Manual Editing Tools', home_feat4_desc: 'Refine your pattern with paint, erase, fill, and eyedropper tools. Undo and redo as many times as you need until the pattern looks exactly right.',
      home_feat5_title: 'Round & Square Drills', home_feat5_desc: 'Switch between round (2.8mm) and square (2.5mm) drills. Each type has different visual characteristics and the tool calculates spacing accordingly.',
      home_feat6_title: 'Export & Save', home_feat6_desc: 'Download your finished pattern as a high-resolution image, or save your work as a project file to continue editing later. Print-ready output included.',
      home_how_label: 'How It Works', home_how_title: 'How to convert a photo to diamond painting in 3 steps', home_how_subtitle: 'No software to install, no account to create. Just open the tool and start creating.',
      home_step1_title: 'Upload Your Photo', home_step1_desc: 'Drag and drop any image — a pet portrait, landscape, family photo, or your own artwork. JPG, PNG, and WebP all work perfectly.',
      home_step2_title: 'Set Your Canvas Size', home_step2_desc: 'Pick a canvas size and adjust the color count. The tool instantly previews your pattern and shows exactly how many beads you will need.',
      home_step3_title: 'Download & Create', home_step3_desc: 'Export your DMC-coded pattern as an image. Order your drills, print your pattern, and enjoy the meditative process of diamond painting.',
      home_how_btn: 'Start Generating Now →',
      home_why_label: 'Why Diamond Painter', home_why_title: 'The free custom diamond painting generator that crafters trust',
      home_why_subtitle: 'Built by someone who knows what it is like to squint at a tiny pattern or waste an order because the color count was off.',
      home_ben1_title: 'Instant Preview', home_ben1_desc: 'See your pattern update live as you adjust settings — no waiting for renders.',
      home_ben2_title: 'Accurate Colors', home_ben2_desc: 'DMC codes are matched using perceptual color distance, not just RGB proximity.',
      home_ben3_title: 'Private & Secure', home_ben3_desc: 'Your photos never leave your device. Processing happens entirely in your browser.',
      home_ben4_title: 'Multilingual', home_ben4_desc: 'Full support for English, Korean, Japanese, and Chinese interfaces.',
      home_learn_label: 'Learn', home_learn_title: 'Diamond painting guides & tutorials',
      home_learn_subtitle: 'Whether you\'re just starting out or looking to improve your technique, our guides cover everything you need to know.',
      home_guide1_tag: 'Beginner', home_guide1_title: 'Complete Beginner\'s Guide to Diamond Painting', home_guide1_desc: 'Everything you need to know before placing your first diamond — materials, technique, and what to expect.', home_guide1_link: 'Read guide →',
      home_guide2_tag: 'Tutorial', home_guide2_title: 'How to Create a Custom Diamond Painting Pattern', home_guide2_desc: 'Step-by-step tutorial on turning your own photos into a custom diamond painting using our free tool.', home_guide2_link: 'Read tutorial →',
      home_guide3_tag: 'Tips', home_guide3_title: '20 Diamond Painting Tips That Actually Work', home_guide3_desc: 'Practical, tested tips for faster progress, fewer mistakes, and a more enjoyable painting experience.', home_guide3_link: 'Read tips →',
      home_view_all_guides: 'View all guides →',
      home_faq_label: 'FAQ', home_faq_title: 'Common questions, honest answers', home_faq_subtitle: 'New to diamond painting? Here are the questions we hear most often from beginners.',
      home_view_all_faqs: 'View all FAQs →',
      home_faq1_q: 'Is Diamond Painter really free?', home_faq1_a: 'Yes, completely free. There are no premium tiers, no watermarks on exports, and no account required. The tool runs entirely in your browser, so there are no server costs passed on to you.',
      home_faq2_q: 'What image types work best?', home_faq2_a: 'High-contrast images with clear focal points produce the best results. Pet portraits, single-subject photos, and simple landscapes typically convert beautifully. Try reducing colors to 20–30 for complex images.',
      home_faq3_q: 'What is a DMC color code?', home_faq3_a: 'DMC (Dollfus-Mieg et Compagnie) is the world\'s most widely used thread and drill numbering system. Diamond painting drills are sold using the same codes, so DMC 321 always refers to the same shade of red across all major suppliers.',
      home_faq4_q: 'What is custom diamond painting?', home_faq4_a: 'Custom diamond painting is a craft where you recreate a personal photo as a mosaic artwork by placing small resin diamonds (drills) onto an adhesive canvas. A diamond painting pattern maker converts your photo into a DMC color-coded chart — every position on the canvas maps to a specific drill color, so you know exactly what to place where.',
      home_faq5_q: 'How do I convert a photo into a diamond painting pattern?', home_faq5_a: 'Simply upload your photo, choose your canvas size and the number of colors (25–40 works well for most images), then click Generate. Diamond Painter instantly converts your photo into a full DMC color-coded diamond painting pattern. Export the result as a printable image — no account or software download needed.',
      home_faq6_q: '보석십자수 도안은 어떻게 만드나요?', home_faq6_a: '사진을 업로드하고 캔버스 크기와 색상 수(보통 25~40개)를 선택한 다음 생성 버튼을 클릭하면 됩니다. DMC 코드가 포함된 보석십자수 도안이 즉시 생성되며, 출력 가능한 이미지로 내보낼 수 있습니다. 완전 무료이며 회원가입이 필요 없습니다.',
      home_cta_label: 'Get Started', home_cta_title: 'Ready to create your first pattern?', home_cta_subtitle: 'No account needed. Open the tool and you are creating in under a minute.',
